Package: markr
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Make MkDocs Documentation for a Package
Description: Converts Rd files to markdown, runs examples, knits vignettes, and parses
             information from the README, DESCRIPTION and CITATION files to build
             package documentation that can be build with MkDocs.
Authors@R: c(person("Jason", "Vander Heiden", role=c("aut", "cre"),
                    email="jason.vanderheiden@yale.edu"),
             person("Hadley", "Wickham", role=c("ctb"),
                    email="hadley@rstudio.com"))
